How to build Yhorn
====================

1. Run `autoconf` to generate `configure`
2. `./configure`
3. `make`
4. If you want to make executables, run either `make yhorn.byte` or
   `make yhorn.opt`
5. For documentation, `make doc` to generate HTML-based one, or `make depgraph`
   to see the dependency graph between modules.
